data.description: This exquisite residence sits on a charming corner lot within the desirable Weatherstone/Mason Park community. Its strategic location places it within a mere couple of miles from a plethora of dining options, cafes, retail stores, and grocery outlets. The community itself boasts a wealth of amenities, including a spacious pool, a delightful play park, tranquil ponds, frequent food truck gatherings, and various other engaging community events. Moreover, the property enjoys exceptional proximity, being just a short 3-mile drive away from key destinations such as I-26, Azalea Square, Downtown Summerville, and Nexton Square. The house itself is a stunning 3-story abode, featuring beautifully tiled porches, including a private one adjoining the master suite, complete with a generousgarden tub and a separate standalone shower.  Furthermore, the third floor of this home offers a versatile bonus room with a closet, lending itself to various potential uses, such as a fifth bedroom, a playroom, a media room, a workout space, or even a home office.
